{"tid":1655154,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔好再重覆犯錯了，想谷人出去就入黎","createTime":"2019-10-15T02:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T01:21:26.000Z","uid":13936,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"4e9701e677a7274426a5823913a9d7e9f0708202","tid":1655154,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:30:08.000Z","msg":"10月20日 民陣終於出手申請遊行<br />\n雖然我認為最後班狗都唔會批不反對，但唔緊要，反正大家都出。<br />\n但係，大家唔好忘記一百萬人同二百萬人出黎既原因<br />\n係呢個遊行用左接近一星期文宣工作去宣傳叫人出去<br />\n包括 一星期內自發多個集會 / 活動  去谷人去遊行<br />\n記唔記得 D 小型集會口號係咩?  6月9日 去遊行!<br />\n大家仲記唔記得個張64 既GIF?  點解上街? 因為責任<br />\n仲有8月5日罷工點解咁成功?  因為用左好耐去宣傳<br />\n記唔記得班手足係香港站跪地叫人罷工?<br />\n記唔記得網絡成班KOL SHARE 叫人遊行集會? <br />\n人地KOL 講一句 = 我地圍爐講一百句<br />\n<br />\n以上所有野全部呢家都唔會出現，我唔知大家懶左定係點<br />\n呢家變得圍爐咁，係連登出張圖 SET 個BOT 就叫出左文宣 出左宣傳<br />\n完全無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時又屌少人 又屌人唔出<br />\n<br />\n我建議 距離10月20日仲有5日時間比我地攪活動宣傳<br />\n一來令抗爭運動持續  二來利用五日落區 攪活動 去宣傳10月20日<br />\n成效大撚過你係連登出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你又唔係唔知連登充斥住靈異 捉鬼 休息 五毛消極撚<br />\n<br />\n如果以上所朕野都唔做<br />\n10月20日都係得好少人出   好少人出  等於班POPO 一開始就打壓  因為你少人聚唔到人呀<br />\n你多人 塞爆 班POPO 基於安全 一定唔撤退由你行 之後先再打算清場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求大家 得返關鍵5日咋"},{"pid":"d5be84570a989ceb8fb51a7723f25200cde883bb","tid":1655154,"uid":157070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:31:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1020見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f011754f38c382f159cc2515f6192e71f1c5356","tid":1655154,"uid":80162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:40:15.000Z","msg":"6月9 去遊行！<br />\n<br />\n返嚟啦大師兄 要有返6月9號嘅感覺呀"},{"pid":"1be017e8dade155c6e1539fa89658b771563f3a8","tid":1655154,"uid":208452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:44:50.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係呀,我知我地講近廢話,但前線的確需要支援<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"d9637b12b4fc8b191f12696b324803b4ed303d5d","tid":1655154,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:45:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a83347be04e067ab06efba9c96ad55597b9dbc9f","tid":1655154,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:46:20.000Z","msg":"要派傳單了"},{"pid":"420d061c6c46230aee5329e374deeb0a68ac6196","tid":1655154,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7MNgLMr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7MNgLMr.png&h=f90ad1a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iNKGcrs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiNKGcrs.png&h=351b8c75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dab2048a901494313423222b7166931a4f0f9fb9","tid":1655154,"uid":205749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:47:18.000Z","msg":"需要傳單！"},{"pid":"ae58f1f817eb16fb58b0a6331eb0ed3940535826